(Learning Objectives) Tj
T*
(- Explain the meaning of Mechanics in Physics using accurate subject vocabulary.) Tj
T*
(- Describe the key ideas behind the main ideas and methods involved in Mechanics.) Tj
T*
(- Apply Mechanics to examples such as a simple classroom example involving Mechanics.) Tj
T*
